Class FastRangeCountOp<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.bop.CoreBaseBOp

          • com.bigdata.bop.join.FastRangeCountOp<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BOp, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class FastRangeCountOp<E>
extends PipelineOp
    This operator reports the fast-range count for an as-bound IPredicate . The cost of this operator is two key probes. Unlike a normal access path, this operator does not bind variables to data in tuples in the underlying index. Instead it binds a pre-identified variable to the aggregate (COUNT) of the tuple range spanned by the IPredicate.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
    See Also:
    Rewrite SELECT COUNT(...) (DISTINCT|REDUCED) {single-triple-pattern} as ESTCARD , Serialized Form
